data.description: Welcome to the Spring Valley Ridge. This Beautiful Spacious Five Bedroom and Three Bathroom Pool Home is your perfect oasis in the desert. Home features 2,741of square feet of living, 7,918 square feet lot, a newly paved driveway leading to RV parking, and a 2-car garage with Newer Epoxy flooring. Entering inside, you are greeted to an open, high ceiling, high window living room and dining area. The natural light makes the home bright and warm. The downstairs conveniently has one bedroom and one full bathroom. The elegant kitchen includes a pantry, ample amount of cabinetry with impressive granite countertops. It opens to the family room with a fireplace and sliding glass door to the  backyard patio area perfect for relaxation or entertainment. Upstairs there are 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The master suite has a large walk-in closet, cozy fireplace, and master bathroom with a jet soaking tub. Also features an oversized balcony to enjoy while looking out at the great mountain view. The backyard features a large premium covered patio including outdoor fan, recessed lighting, and mounted TV, great for hanging out near the pool. The backyard is very low maintenance with turf and paver upgrades. It also looks out to a view of the desert with no back neighbors, which is absolutely beautiful at sunset. NO HOA in this desirable neighborhood. Close to VVC College, Endeavor School of Exploration, and shopping centers. Conveniently located for commuting, via newly opened Yucca Loma Rd/Green Tree Blvd. This home will not last long on the market. Schedule a private showing today!
